ga-3 triglycerides, in an easy to swallow, mini capsule.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Omega Platinum Mini All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Omega Platinum Mini Size Size 50 capsules Blackmores Omega Platinum Mini, Blackmores highest strength mini capsule – omega-3 your everyday essential. Blackmores Omega Platinum Mini delivers a high-strength dose of concentrated omega-3 triglycerides, expertly formulated into a mini capsule to support 10 essential health benefits in one convenient, easy-to-swallow capsule. With enhanced levels of DHA and EPA, this premium supplement helps: • Maintain brain health and cognitive function • Maintain Eye health and healthy vision • Relieve symptoms of mild osteoarthritis • Maintain heart health and cardiovascular health • Plus, it has additional benefits for skin and overall vitality Designed for those who want more from every capsule, Omega Platinum Mini combines potency with convenience so you can get more out of your day, your health, and your life. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Heart and Cardiovascular Health Brain Health Eye Health Skin Health Mild Arthritis No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Available now at Chemist Warehouse. Shop here . Supports vitality, general health and wellbeing. Maintains brain health. Maintains eye health and function. Supports cardiovascular system health. Maintains skin health when dietary intake is inadequate. Relieves inflammation and supports symptoms of mild arthritis. Reduces free radicals from the body. Supports nervous system health. Dosage Adults Take 2 capsules once a day. To support immune system health and healthy mood balance: Take 2 capsules two times a day. Do not exceed 4 capsules in 24 hours. Take with Food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish products, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Available now at Chemist Warehouse. Shop here . Supports vitality, general health and wellbeing. Maintains brain health. Maintains eye health and function. Supports cardiovascular system health. Maintains skin health when dietary intake is inadequ