ys a role in protecting retinal tissues and helps maintain healthy eyesight in ageing individuals. Taken daily, Macu-Vision® helps defend your eye cells from oxidative stress and supports your long-term vision goals. Good health changes everything - support your eyes every day with Blackmores Macu-Vision®. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Macula Health Eye Health No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Helps support eye macula health. Supports healthy vision. Supports eye health. Antioxidant to reduce free radicals in the body. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. WARNING - Contains zinc, which may be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period of time. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Helps support eye macula health. Supports healthy vision. Supports eye health. Antioxidant to reduce free radicals in the body. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet once a day or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. WARNING - Contains zinc, which may be dangerous if taken in large amounts or for a long period of time. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. S